OL,3,CSerial killer who confessed to
OL,4,Cmurdering 42 women escapes custody
OL,6,FA man who confessed to killing 42
OL,7,Fwomen and was detained after the
OL,8,Fdiscovery of numerous dismembered
OL,9,Fbodies has escaped police custody in
OL,10,FKenya.
OL,12,FCollins Jumaisi Khalusha, 33, escaped
OL,13,Falong with 12 other inmates of
OL,14,FEritrean nationality who had been
OL,15,Farrested for being in the country
OL,16,Fillegally, the head of the Directorate
OL,17,Fof Criminal Investigations said on
OL,18,FTuesday.
