OL,3,CSerial killer who confessed to
OL,4,Cmurdering 42 women escapes custody
OL,6,FActing police inspector general
OL,7,FGilbert Masengeli said disciplinary
OL,8,Fmeasures have been taken against eight
OL,9,Fofficers, including the area and
OL,10,Fstation commanders and officers who
OL,11,Fwere on duty.
OL,13,F"Our preliminary investigations
OL,14,Findicate that the escape was aided by
OL,15,Finsiders considering that officers
OL,16,Fwere deployed accordingly to guard the
OL,17,Fstation," he said.
