OL,3,CSerial killer who confessed to
OL,4,Cmurdering 42 women escapes custody
OL,6,FA police report said the inmates
OL,7,Fescaped early on Tuesday morning after
OL,8,Fthey cut through wire mesh in the cell
OL,9,Fand scaled the perimeter wall. The
OL,10,Fescape was discovered as breakfast was
OL,11,Fbeing taken into the cell.
OL,13,FKhalusha was being detained at the
OL,14,Fpolice station after a court allowed
OL,15,Fdetectives seven more days to
OL,16,Finvestigate his alleged crimes before
OL,17,Fcharging him.
