OL,3,CSerial killer who confessed to
OL,4,Cmurdering 42 women escapes custody
OL,6,FHe was arrested in July after 10
OL,7,Fbodies and several body parts were
OL,8,Ffound wrapped in plastic sacks in the
OL,9,FKware area of Nairobi. Police said
OL,10,FKhalusha confessed to killing 42
OL,11,Fwomen, including his wife.
OL,13,F"This was a high-value suspect who was
OL,14,Fto face serious charges. We are
OL,15,Finvestigating the incident and will
OL,16,Ftake action accordingly," Mohamed
OL,17,FAmin, the head of the Directorate of
OL,18,FCriminal Investigations, said.
