OL,3,CSerial killer who confessed to
OL,4,Cmurdering 42 women escapes custody
OL,6,FThe police station from which the
OL,7,Fsuspects escaped was cordoned off with
OL,8,Fcrime scene tape and senior police
OL,9,Fofficers visited it on Tuesday
OL,10,Fafternoon.
OL,12,FTwo other suspects who were arrested
OL,13,Fafter being found with cellphones
OL,14,Fbelonging to some of the deceased
OL,15,Fwomen are to return to court next
OL,16,FMonday.
