OL,3,CSerial killer who confessed to
OL,4,Cmurdering 42 women escapes custody
OL,6,FIn July police said the bodies were
OL,7,Fdiscovered after relatives of one
OL,8,Fmissing woman said they had a dream in
OL,9,Fwhich she told them to search in a
OL,10,Fquarry.
OL,12,FThe relatives asked a local diver to
OL,13,Fhelp and he discovered the bodies
OL,14,Fwrapped in sacks. Six bodies were
OL,15,Fidentified after DNA tests, but
OL,16,Fseveral body parts remain unidentified.
